### Variables
@baseUrl = https://qjfygjtondljywhbqbfj.supabase.co/functions/v1
@authToken = YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE
@clientToken = CLIENT_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

### Test 1 - Rejeter un devis avec raison (cas nominal)
POST {{baseUrl}}/quotes-reject-quote
Authorization: Bearer {{clientToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "quote_id": "quote-uuid-here",
  "reason": "Budget trop élevé"
}

### Test 2 - Rejeter un devis sans raison
POST {{baseUrl}}/quotes-reject-quote
Authorization: Bearer {{clientToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "quote_id": "quote-uuid-here"
}

### Test 3 - Erreur: quote_id manquant
POST {{baseUrl}}/quotes-reject-quote
Authorization: Bearer {{clientToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{}

### Test 4 - Erreur: devis déjà accepté
POST {{baseUrl}}/quotes-reject-quote
Authorization: Bearer {{clientToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "quote_id": "already-accepted-quote-uuid"
}

### Test 5 - Erreur: devis déjà rejeté
POST {{baseUrl}}/quotes-reject-quote
Authorization: Bearer {{clientToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "quote_id": "already-rejected-quote-uuid"
}

